  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1006313/" class="title-link">说不上完美，但是好文字</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1006313"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/xiangshanjumu/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1027926-1.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/xiangshanjumu/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">向山举目</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2005-10-06"
      class="main-meta">2005-10-06 12:42:54</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1006313_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                      因为朋友的推荐，买了这本小书。原来一直想买汪曾祺全集的，所以，对这类选集并不十分在意。然而这本山东画报出版的小书，从卖相上来说，就很吸引我这种严重“以貌取书”的人了。 从顶部向底端方向近4/5的橙黄色，留白处左下角一串水墨画的豆角（或其他豆类植物）的藤架。...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">8有用 / 2没用</span>
